<HEAD>Brown Moves Toward Democratic Chairmanship</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Democrats rallied around Ronald Brown Thursday
as the Washington attorney moved toward the party chairmanship.
   Former Rep. James Stanton of Ohio, one of his rivals for the
