``for farming and farming only,'' Best said.
   The land is near the Lincoln Log Cabin State Historic Site, and
several volunteers who work at the restored Lincoln Log Cabin showed
up in period costumes.
   Though the character of Thomas Lincoln, who actually farmed the
land, was represented, Abe Lincoln was not.
