Equipment climbed 3\ to 114~; International Business Machines 3 to
126\, and Hewlett-Packard 1| to 57].
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks gained
1.10 to 163.43. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up 1.56 at 321.06.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 168.29 million shares with an
hour to go.
